patch.description:
All quote item fields and custom fields need to be editable before sending request.<br />

Fields with invalid values are returned in the response in the following format:<br />
```
    {
        "ItemFields": {
            "FieldName": "ErrorMessage",
            "FieldName2": "ErrorMessage"
        }
     }
```
Fields with valid values will be updated and not included in the response.

Quote item custom fields of type Date need to be in the format "yyyy-MM-dd".

